    "Several methods have been developed for diagnosing diseases to minimize serious harm.",
    "Molecular biology techniques, in particular, offer precise identification of pathogenic factors.",
    "Many farmers may not have access to these methods, though, and they are expensive and resource-intensive to obtain or execute (Sahu et al. 2021).",
